{"tid":914177,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【中國在南海浪花礁建新平台】 【美智庫：或涉軍事用途】","createTime":"2018-11-24T05:04:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-24T05:10:05.000Z","uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4ac049b43edcc333be4465e61e6746f8ef80a6a7","tid":914177,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T05:04:28.000Z","msg":"【中國在南海浪花礁建新平台】<br />\n【美智庫：或涉軍事用途】<br />\n<br />\n美國戰略與國際研究中心屬下「亞洲海事透明倡議」，發布多張衛星圖片。<br />\n<br />\n見到一個長 27 米，闊 12 米的新平台，頂部有天線和太陽能板。<br />\n<br />\n智庫指，平台今年 7 月初出現，估計內藏其他設施。<br />\n<br />\n相對一般浮標，平台看起來較大及複雜，又指浪花礁毗鄰西沙群島及南沙群島間的主要航道，有利中國擴大雷達偵測範圍及收集情報。<br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部指，不了解具體情況，但強調西沙群島是中國領土，中方在領土上開展建設活動無可非議。<br />\n<br />\n越南批評是嚴重侵犯越南主權。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/287143318581885/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fvideos%2F287143318581885%2F&d=uJJZkqHGH4AVduFxQmeqIsP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=f2dbc3cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/287143318581885/</a>"},{"pid":"175e66a53b5f64027485c389c259643e5954d528","tid":914177,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T05:09:37.000Z","msg":"G20唔撚使有deal做到啦咁。"},{"pid":"4aee3ffe6c1bf710c73c6d58494d8703c042c0c3","tid":914177,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T05:10:05.000Z","msg":"明落美國面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}